item.title: [PI] problems
item.dc:creator: @emtrescue emtrescue
item.description:

replace java with your classpath

ex:

title RunServer "C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jdk1.6.0_26\bin\java.exe" -Xmx512m -cp .;./jython.jar;./MySql/mysql-connector-java-3.0.18-ga-bin.jar;.\AllGoFreePortForwarding.jar server cls exit

btw, dont use this one eaxtly its for deltascape
